text.section:
The resolution shall set forth:
The class of stockholders who may certify;
The purpose for which the certification may be made;
The form of certification and the information to be contained in it;
If the certification is with respect to a record date or closing of the stock transfer books, the time after the record date or closing of the stock transfer books within which the certification must be received by the corporation; and
Any other provisions with respect to the procedure which the board considers necessary or desirable.
